#Text=I believe in discipline and respect for teachers and administrators , but I believe in school choice .
#Text=I do n’t believe in the Teacher ’s Unions taking teachers monies and lobbying in Washington on causes that the Teachers may not believe in .
#Text=I would enact Child Support Revisions to help good Dads who take care of their children without the government interfering .

#Text=I would enact a Private Medical CO-OP that pays dividends for those who remain healthily while we pay for whatever health problems the sick may have , with no co-pays and including all dental , vision home care , long term and short term care .
#Text=This plan may have some government oversight by the Attorney General .
#Text=Campaigning for the American presidency is one of the most expensive exercises in the world .
#Text=How do you deal with the cost and fundraising ?
#Text=I do n’t have an expert to fundraise for me , so I campaign over the internet and YouTube .
#Text=I travel when the funds are available .
#Text=I 'm reaching people in France and all over America .
#Text=They are shocked that I respond to them , when I 'm not out physically campaigning or doing interviews .
#Text=People would support me if I were on the news and was getting support that way .
#Text=Do you have a running mate yet ?
#Text=Who are they ?
#Text=What are you looking for in a running mate ?
#Text=I do n’t yet have a running mate .
#Text=They have to care about our country and not try to be positioning for a powerful position .
#Text=They have to want to take care of business and carry out my platform and be objective .
#Text=I do n’t like “ yes ” people .
#Text=I can deal with constructive criticism , because the things I ’m doing are to better our country .
#Text=The More Than A Woman ” Presidential Campaign is not about me .
#Text=It ’s about us “ WE The People ” and how we can pursue happiness without so much Government Interference .
#Text=Can you win the 2008 Presidential election ?

#Text=Yes , if I had the same media coverage and had been invited to participate in the debates the News Media have and are sponsoring for only Republicans or Democrats and their so-called Front runners , yet excluding the Independent Candidate .
#Text=I 've proven what I can do on Fox News 's The O'Reilly Factor .
#Text=Feel free to look at the actual segment on my Presidential Website www.rbwforpres2008.com .
#Text=Fox received thousands of emails from people who said they liked what I had to say about the issue I was talking about .
#Text=People want to see me on the news programs , because I have the answers to the problems most ca n't figure out
#Text=Can any third party or independent candidate ever win ?
#Text=Yes , especially if the National news would stop being so partisan .
#Text=At least the voters would know every Candidate running and their platforms .
#Text=If 57 % of the people are Independents that means the voters are being disenfranchised all over the country .
#Text=The voters have the right and yet have no idea they can vote for any of us 100+ Candidate out there .
#Text=I will make sure they know .
#Text=Why not ?
